section.def:
Board
                (委員會) means the Antiquities Advisory Board
            established by section 17;

licence
                (牌照) means a licence granted under section
                13;

permit
                (許可證) means a permit granted under section
                6;

subparagraph.content:
serve on the owner and any lawful occupier of the private land a copy
                        of the notice of declaration, together with a copy of the plan;
                        and

paragraph.content:
knowingly makes a false statement to the Authority or to a designated
                    person as to the situation or circumstances of the discovery of an
                    antiquity;

without reasonable excuse, fails to comply with a request made to him by
                    the Authority or a designated person under section 11(2);
                    or
